Bloomberg published an article I wrote called

213
0:10:23.217,000 --> 0:10:27,000
"The Capitalist’s Case for a $15 Minimum Wage."

214
0:10:28.15,000 --> 0:10:3,000
The good people at Forbes magazine,

215
0:10:31.072,000 --> 0:10:33,000
among my biggest admirers,

216
0:10:33.27,000 --> 0:10:37,000
called it "Nick Hanauer's near-insane proposal."

217
0:10:37.99,000 --> 0:10:4,000
And yet, just 350 days

218
0:10:41.219,000 --> 0:10:43,000
