219
0:10:43.795,000 --> 0:10:45,000
Seattle's Mayor Ed Murray signed into law

220
0:10:46.744,000 --> 0:10:49,000
an ordinance raising the minimum wage in Seattle

221
0:10:50.51,000 --> 0:10:51,000
to 15 dollars an hour,

222
0:10:52.198,000 --> 0:10:53,000
more than double

223
0:10:53.638,000 --> 0:10:57,000
what the prevailing federal $7.25 rate is.

224
0:10:58.33,000 --> 0:10:59,000
How did this happen,

225
0:11:00.11,000 --> 0:11:02,000
reasonable people might ask.

226
0:11:02.195,000 --> 0:11:03,000
It happened because a group of us

227
0:11:03.863,000 --> 0:11:04,000
